	</style>
		<table style="border-bottom:2px solid black; font-weight:bold; font-size:120%; cellspacing:0; cellpadding:0;">
			<tr>
				<td align="left" >NOTICE FOR CONTROLLERS</td>
				<td align="right" > Annex B</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="height:5px;"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

		<!-- <td width="52">&nbsp;</td> -->

		<p style=" text-align: left; text-decoration: underline; font-weight:bold; font-size:100%;">Date of Notice: <b>{% if datas.field_company_effect_date is not null %}{{ datas.field_company_effect_date|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</b><br/><br/></p>
		<p style="font-weight:bold; text-align: left;">Dear {{datas.officer.field_full_name}}</p>

		<p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> We know or have reasonable grounds to believe that you are a registrable controller of <b>{{ datas.company_name }} {{ datas.field_company_type }}</b></p>

		<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> This notice is sent under section 386AG(2)(a) of the Companies Act (Cap. 50) and requires you to
provide the following information within 30 days after the date of this notice.</p>

    <p style=" text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> Please send your reply to {{ datas.field_address_line_1 }} {{ datas.field_address_line_2 }} {{ datas.field_postcode }}. Failure to provide the information required by this
notice may be an offence.</p>

    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> 1. Are you a registrable controller of <b>{{ datas.company_name }} {{ datas.field_company_type }}</b>?</p>
    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  14em;"> Your reply: Yes / <del>No</del> </p>
    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> * Delete as appropriate. If your reply is yes and you are an individual, please provide the particulars in sub-paragraph
      (a). If your reply is yes and you are a legal entity, please provide the particulars in sub-paragraph (b).
    </p>

		<p style="text-align: left;">(a) If your reply is yes and you are an individual, please provide the following particulars: </p>

		<table cellpadding="3px">
			<tr>
				<td colspan="5" class="toptd" >Individual Information</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Full name (including any alias)</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{datas.officer.field_full_name}} </td>
			</tr>
			<tr >
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Address (residential/ place of business/ registered office)</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{datas.officer.field_address_line_1}} {{datas.officer.field_address_line_2}} {{datas.officer.field_postal_code}}  </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Nationality</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{ datas.officer.field_nationality }} </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
			  <td colspan="2" class="bd">ID / Passport Number</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{datas.officer.field_id_type}} {{datas.officer.field_id_no}} </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Date of Birth</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{datas.officer.field_date_of_birth|date('d/m/Y')}} </td>
			</tr>

			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Contact number</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{{datas.officer.field_mobile}} </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">The date on which you become an individual controller</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">{% if datas.officer.field_date_appointed_registrable is not null %}{{ datas.officer.field_date_appointed_registrable|date('d/m/Y') }}{% endif %}</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

		<br/>
		<p style="text-align: left;"><br/>
		<p style="text-align: left;">(b) If your reply is yes and you are a legal entity, please provide the following particulars: </p>

		<table cellpadding="3px">
			<tr>
				<td colspan="5" class="toptd" >Legal Entity Information</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Full name (including any alias)</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">  </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Address (residential/ place of business/ registered office)</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">   </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Nationality</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">  </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
			  <td colspan="2" class="bd">ID / Passport Number</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">  </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Date of Birth</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">  </td>
			</tr>

			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">Contact number</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd">  </td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2" class="bd">The date on which you become an individual controller</td>
				<td colspan="3" class="bd"> </td>
			</tr>
		</table>	 </p>

    <br/>
		<p style="text-align: left;"><br/>
		<p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> 2. Do you know or have reasonable grounds to believe that any other person is a registrable
controller of <b>{{ datas.company_name }} {{ datas.field_company_type }}</b> or is likely to have that knowledge?
    </p>
    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  14em;"> Your reply: <del>Yes</del> / No </p>


    <p style="text-align: left;">In this notice —</p>


    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> “controller”, “corporate controller”, “individual controller” and “legal entity” have the meanings
given to them in section 386AB of the Companies Act;</p>
    <p style="text-align:justify; text-indent:  8em;"> “identity card” has the meaning given to it in section 2(1) of the National Registration
Act (Cap. 201); “registrable” has the meaning given to it in section 386AC of the Companies Act.</p>
    <p style="text-align: left;"><h3>SECRETARY</h3></p>
    <table border="0" cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width="90%" align="center">
      <tr><td colspan="3" style="height:20px;"></td></tr>
      {% for secretories in datas.secretory %}
        {% if loop.index % 2 == 1 %}
          <tr>
          <td style="width:40%; text-align:left;font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color: white; font-size: 0.1px">_____________________________________________________________________
                ___________________________________________{{ secretories.signature }}</span>
            <hr><b>{{ secretories.full_name }}</b> <br/>
            SECRETARY
            <br/><br/>
            <br/><br/>
          </td>
          <td width="140"></td>
        {% else %}
          <td style="width:40%; text-align:left;font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color: white; font-size: 0.1px">_____________________________________________________________________
                ___________________________________________{{ secretories.signature }}</span>
            <hr><b>{{ secretories.full_name }}</b> <br/>
            SECRETARY
            <br/><br/>
            <br/><br/>
          </td>
          </tr>
        {% endif %}
        {% if loop.index % 2 == 1 and loop.index == loop.length %}
          <td>
            &nbsp;
          </td>
          </tr>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </table>
	<p style="font-weight:bold; text-align: left;"><h3>CONTROLLER</H3></p>
		<table border="0" cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width="90%" align="center">
		  <tr><td colspan="3" style="height:20px;"></td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="width:40%; text-align:left;font-size:14px;">
          <span style="color: white; font-size: 1px">_____________________________________________________________________
          ___________________________________________{{ datas.share_holder.signature }}</span>
          <hr><b>{{ datas.share_holder.full_name }}</b> <br/>
          CONTROLLER
          <br/>Date:<br/>
          <br/><br/>
        </td>
      </tr>
	  </table>

</body>
</html>
